Description

Write a program to print the hollow square pattern.

Input Format

Input consists of one integer that corresponds to the number of rows and columns.

Output Format

Output prints the hollow square pattern for the given number of rows and columns.

Sample Input 1

5

Sample Output 1

*****

*  *

*  *

*  *

*****

CODE:

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner s=new Scanner(System.in);
        int n=s.nextInt();
        for(int i=1;i<=n;i++){
            for(int j=1;j<=n;j++){
               if(i==1||i==n||j==1 ||j==n){
            System.out.print("*");
            }
            else{
                System.out.print(" ");
            }
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}

